rComments: Overall a good prof, quite funny.. but he has a subtle sense of humour. Took the time to answer questions posted on facebook, which was really great of him! Also always happy to further clarify lecture content or discuss something related to course.

He talked very fast so I had to relisten to all of his recordings. Also he gave off the feeling that he didn't prepare the lectures slides himself and were substituting for another prof because he would take slides out during the lecture. But on the actual midterm and tests his questions were pretty fair and straight from the lecture notes.
Very fun prof. His section is interesting too about males and females. He explains very well and clear. Really enjoyed his class. The midterm was hard though because of French's questions.
